{"tid":1828420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底台灣幾時由「北藍南綠」變到「市綠鄉藍」？","createTime":"2020-01-17T20:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T07:15:28.000Z","uid":52658,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f86e50cbc18c8dde7327ac7fc8ad9e5ec5632d6c","tid":1828420,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T20:35:04.000Z","msg":"曾經陳水扁時期既民進黨<br />\n民進黨係比人笑做鄉巴佬 無腦糞青<br />\n果陣既綠都 國民黨穩定佔有4個<br />\n係呢2屆選舉 六都總統票綠都完勝藍<br />\n台北市為例<br />\n以前國民黨就算派粒石頭去選 都拎到60趴票數<br />\n最近呢兩屆選舉<br />\n蔡英文係台北市都贏朱立倫同韓國瑜<br />\n今屆區域仲要淪落到4:4同國民黨打成平手<br />\n第5席仲爭d比吳怡農贏埋添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不分區仲要泛綠43趴對泛藍40趴 輸鳩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左金門馬祖 台東同苗栗之外 <br />\n全台一片綠油油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底國民黨呢幾年是在哈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無熟台灣政治既人解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gZ8Gzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gZ8Gzz.jpg&h=70790de2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67b8913424590eb3e1e3a634596bfcce5acea051","tid":1828420,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T20:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b1dc93e678c77a85469f696b18c14d3b753421","tid":1828420,"uid":198258,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T21:52:57.000Z","msg":"因為美國出左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e03aa03af377601d32ed7f33a360d6d0eaba93f","tid":1828420,"uid":261913,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"quote":{"pid":"a5b1dc93e678c77a854